# NOTE: packages/worker/wrangler.toml IS tracked on purpose. It contains only
# non-sensitive identifiers (D1 database_id, Google OAuth client_id, public
# bucket/URL names). All real secrets (JWT_SECRET, SLACK_BOT_TOKEN,
# PANANAMES_SIGNATURE, GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET) live as encrypted Cloudflare
# Secrets — never in this file. account_id is intentionally omitted.

